{
  "id": "adv_event_2109_01_01",
  "title": "LizNoir失格",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、今日は来てくれてありがとう！\n最後までついてきて頂戴！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone! Thank you for coming today!\nPlease stay with us to the end!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2333333333333334,
      "endTime": 7.199999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 2.2333333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きゃああああっ！　LizNoir、サイコー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yahhhh! LizNoir are the best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4,
      "endTime": 11.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 13
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "私達の歌とダンスでこんなに盛り上がってくれて\n私……凄く嬉しい！　凄く楽しい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m really happy that you’re so pumped up\nby our singing and dancing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.066666666666666,
      "endTime": 23.301430638631185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 23.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "私、もっと歌いたい！　もっと踊りたい！\nもっと、もっと、もっと……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to sing and dance much more!\nMore‚ more‚ and more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3,
      "endTime": 30.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.766666666666666,
      "endTime": 32.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……どうしよう……\n莉央さんがあんなに怒るなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh* What should I do?\nRio-san is so fuRio-sanus…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 40.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり私はリズノワにふさわしくないのかな……\nアイドルに向いてないのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe I’m not a good fit for LizNoir after all…\nMaybe I’m not cut out to be an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.666666666666664,
      "endTime": 47.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、愛？\nため息なんてついてどうしたのですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Ai?\nWhy are you sighing like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.233333333333334,
      "endTime": 53.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 199.99999999999574
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、すずちゃん……\nえっと……ちょっと考え事を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Suzu-chan…\nErm… I had something on my mind…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6,
      "endTime": 59.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "悩みがあるのなら、今をときめくスーパーアイドル\n成宮すずが相談に乗って差し上げますわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If something’s worrying you‚ I’ll allow you to consult with\nthe sparkling super idol Suzu Narumiya.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5,
      "endTime": 66.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "心配してくれてありがとうございます\nすずちゃんって優しいんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for caring about me.\nYou’re kind‚ Suzu-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.8,
      "endTime": 72.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、その通りですわ！\n私の半分は優しさで出来ているのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I really am!\nAt least half of me is made of pure kindness!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.86666666666666,
      "endTime": 78.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "それで何を悩んでいるのかしら？\nスーパーアイドルの私に話してみなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what’s bothering you?\nPlease‚ talk to me‚ the super idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.2,
      "endTime": 85.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "実は……昨日、ライブがあったんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The thing is… we had a show yesterday…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.56666666666666,
      "endTime": 89.46666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 90.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "愛、今日のステージの貴方は酷かったわ\n一人だけ踊りがまるで合っていなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ you act just too much on stage today.\nYour dancing was totally out of step with the rest of us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.76666666666667,
      "endTime": 98.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 95.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 98.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "感情を前面に出して踊るのがダメとは言わないわ\nでも興奮して周りが見えなくなるなんて論外よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not saying it’s wrong to dance with your emotions showing‚\nbut getting so excited that you ignore everyone else is out of the question.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5,
      "endTime": 105.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 106.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "貴方は自分の楽しさを優先して\n観に来てくれたファンをないがしろにしたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You put your own fun first‚\nand neglected the fans who came to see us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.2,
      "endTime": 111.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ファンへの思いやりを忘れた貴方は\nLizNoir失格よ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Forgetting to care for your fans makes you\nunfit for LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.46666666666667,
      "endTime": 115.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoir失格だなんて\n莉央さんもきついことを言いますわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Unfit for LizNoir‚”\nRio-san can say some harsh things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9,
      "endTime": 124.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "そう言いたくなるくらい私に失望したんだと思います\n私って本当にダメダメですから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She must be so disappointed in me that it prompted her to say that.\nBecause I really am no good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.6,
      "endTime": 132.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "昨日だって莉央さんと合わせて踊っているうちに\n楽しい気持ちが抑えきれなくなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yesterday while I was dancing with Rio-san‚\nI couldn’t keep the feeling of fun in me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.56666666666666,
      "endTime": 138.96666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして愛は莉央さんのファンなのですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ are you a fan of Rio-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.16666666666666,
      "endTime": 143.33333333333331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "ファンと言うより、ずっと憧れていた存在です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it’s more that I’ve always admired her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 147.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんはThe Last Chanceという\n楽曲を知っていますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do Suzu-chan know the song\n“The Last Chance”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148,
      "endTime": 151.83333333333331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "確か、リズノワがまだ莉央さんと葵の\n二人組だった頃の曲ですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was back when LizNoir was just\nRio-san and Aoi as a duo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 157.53333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "あの曲の「燃え上がるよ、そこへ行きたいよ」と\nいう歌詞が私は特に好きで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I particularly liked the lyric “I’m burning up‚ I want to go there”\nin that song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8,
      "endTime": 163.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワがいる場所に私もいつか行くんだと\n曲を聴いて自分を奮い立たせていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listening to that song encourages me.\nI tell myself I’ll eventually reach where LizNoir were.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 170.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
