      "text": "莉央さんが歌うあの曲は、私にとって特別な……\n辛い時に心を支えてくれた宝物のような曲なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That song‚ sung by Rio-san‚ is special for me…\nIt’s like a treasure that’s supported me emotionally in hard times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.73333333333332,
      "endTime": 180.33333333333331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
