      "text": "辛い時、心の支えになる曲ってありますわよね\n私にとっては麻奈様の曲がそうでしたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have songs to support my emotions in hard times.\nFor me‚ Mana-sama’s songs were like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.13333333333333,
      "endTime": 191.86666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
